      <div class="home-first--title">Heather Ross,<br />Instructional Design Specialist</div>
      <div class="home-first--subtitle">University of Saskatchewan</div>

      <p>I work closely with Faculty around open textbook and OER for curriculum development.  I think OER should be about making the learning experience better for students.   Creating access for more students and lowering costs is great but the fact that we can adapt materials allows us to make the learning so much better.</p>
